Dependencies
------------

 * python >= 2.6
 * lunch (>= 0.3.2)
 * scenic-utils (>= 0.6.2)
 * python-gtk2
 * python-twisted-core
 * python-txosc (>= 0.1.3)
 * spinframework (>= 0.3.3)
 * jack-tools (>= 0.0.2)
 * jackd

Most of those can be found on SAT's Metalab PPA for Ubuntu Lucid.


Compatibility with SPIN
-----------------------

It is meant to work with the SPIN framework but does not require it for the compilation nor does it need it to be installed on the same computer. It will parse is include/spinFramework/spinDefaults.h file though, if present.


Installation
------------

Type this:

 ./autogen.sh
 ./configure
 make 
 sudo make install


Install on Ubuntu GNU/Linux
---------------------------

Some of its dependencies are on the SAT Metalab archive for Ubuntu GNU/Linux. 
Here is how to install them easily:

 sudo add-apt-repository ppa:sat-metalab/metalab
 sudo apt-get update
 sudo apt-get install scenic lunch python-txosc

